//-
  Ok, this is really dumb, but because we have a sql database with fields set up for beer,
  we have to re-map some mead fields into "non-relevant" beer fields. The mappings are as follows:

  Info:
  Carbonation appearance_head_other
  Sweetness	mouthfeel_creaminess
  Strength	mouthfeel_warmth
  Honey Varietal	appearance_texture_comment

  Aroma:
  Honey		aroma_malt
  Alcohol		aroma_hops
  Fermentation	aroma_fermentation
  Complexity	mouthfeel_astringency		

  Appearance:
  Color		appearance_color
  Clarity		appearance_clarity
  Legs		appearance_head
  Carbonation	appearance_retention

  Flavor:
  Honey		flavor_malt
  Sweetness	flavor_hops
  Acidity		flavor_bitterness
  Tannin		flavor_fermentation
  Alcohol		flavor_balance
  Carbonation	mouthfeel_carbonation
  Body		mouthfeel_body / mouthfeel_other_comment
  Aftertaste	flavor_finish_aftertaste

  Descriptors:
  Acetic 		descriptor_acetaldehyde
  Acidic 		descriptor_alcoholic
  Alcohol 	descriptor_astringent
  Cardboard 	descriptor_brettanomyces
  Chemical 	descriptor_diacetyl
  Cloudy 		descriptor_dms
  Cloying 	descriptor_estery
  floral 		descriptor_grassy
  Fruity/Estery descriptor_lightstruck
  Harsh 		descriptor_metallic
  Metallic 	descriptor_musty
  Moldy 		descriptor_oxidized
  Phenolic 	descriptor_phenolic
  Sherry 		descriptor_solvent
  Solvent 	descriptor_smoky
  Sulfury 	descriptor_sour
  Sweet 		descriptor_spicy
  Tannic 		descriptor_sulfur
  Thin 		descriptor_vegetal
  Vegetal 	mouthfeel_body_inappropriate
  Waxy 		mouthfeel_carbonation_inappropriate
  Yeasty 		descriptor_yeasty

